/*(* must be at the top so that it has the lowest priority *)*/
%nonassoc SHIFTHERE

%nonassoc Telse

%left TOrLog
%left TAndLog
%left TOr
%left TXor
%left TAnd
%left TEqEq TNotEq
%left TInf TSup TInfEq TSupEq
